//Do while loops

import java.util.Scanner;
class Main
{
    public static void main(String args[])
    {
        int i = 0;
        do
        {
             System.out.println("Correct");
             i++;
        }
        while(i<5);
        {
           
        }
       
    }    
}

Do while loops is generally used when we want to print a value once even without executing any sentence or statement.

